L'Oreal Paris Colour Caresse Wet Shine Lip Stain, Pink Resistance, 0.21 Ounces
description: Discover a stain that thinks it's a gloss. Now hydration and shine meet lasting, lightweight color. title: Gold Premium 4 Piece Synthetic Kabuki Makeup Brush Set From Royal Care Cosmetics
description:

Small Flat Kabuki that can be used for liquid or cream foundation application.
